🛠️ Usage
🔹 Hide Data

Select a cover file (image/audio/video/any).

Select or type your secret text/file.

Enter a password.

Click Hide → Encrypted data will be embedded.

🔹 Extract Data

Select a stego file.

Enter the correct password.

Click Extract → Preview & save hidden content.

🔒 Security

All data is encrypted with AES-256-GCM before embedding.

Wrong password = Access Denied animation.

No raw extraction possible without correct key.

📌 Future Improvements

Cloud sharing support.

Mobile app (Android/iOS).

Multi-layer steganography.

🤝 Contributing

Pull requests are welcome. For major changes, please open an issue first to discuss what you would like to change.
